{"talk":{"id":1816,"name":"George Monbiot: For more wonder, rewild the world","description":"Wolves were once native to the US' Yellowstone National Park -- until hunting wiped them out. But when, in 1995, the wolves began to come back (thanks to an aggressive management program), something interesting happened: the rest of the park began to find a new, more healthful balance. In a bold thought experiment, George Monbiot imagines a wilder world in which humans work to restore the complex, lost natural food chains that once surrounded us.","slug":"george_monbiot_for_more_wonder_rewild_the_world","recorded_at":"2013-07-08 00:00:00","published_at":"2013-09-09 15:14:58","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:43:49","viewed_count":983911,"emailed_count":270,"event":{"id":241,"name":"TEDGlobal 2013"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b4a648817c1a2102dc53dc2147bb1af2785067f0_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b4a648817c1a2102dc53dc2147bb1af2785067f0_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b4a648817c1a2102dc53dc2147bb1af2785067f0_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"1600x1200","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b4a648817c1a2102dc53dc2147bb1af2785067f0_1600x1200.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":false,"media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GeorgeMonbiot_2013G-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7464955,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GeorgeMonbiot_2013G-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":20676229,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GeorgeMonbiot_2013G-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":36657363,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GeorgeMonbiot_2013G-450k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4